    "updated_at": "2024-03-09T12:14:09Z",
    "body": "I found a way, you can disable the Nushell character, and keep use Starship character\r\n\r\n```sh\r\nuse starship.nu\r\n$env.PROMPT_INDICATOR_VI_INSERT = \"\"\r\n$env.PROMPT_INDICATOR_VI_NORMAL = \"\"\r\n```\r\n\r\nBut the [`vimcmd_symbol` config in Starship does not work.](https://github.com/starship/starship/issues/4897)",
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "pin": null,
